  "description": "Classic funk stab — tight saw with a short, punchy envelope and moderate bounce rate that gives each 16th note a percussive tail. The prism is parked low: just enough shimmer to add air without losing the pocket. Sits perfectly under a drum machine. RTJ × Chic.",
